{"id":283284,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/【图说天朝】真他妈刺激/","date":"2013-03-11T03:59:03Z","modified":"2013-03-12T06:12:06Z","title":"【图说天朝】真他妈刺激","content":"<p>近日，广东揭西当局出动大批警力包围因土地纠纷出现示威对峙的上浦村，引发暴力冲突。据悉，有多位村民在冲突中受伤，警方在冲突中使用了催泪瓦斯等武器。昨日，一位执行任务的警察还在微博发表了他的“镇压感想”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/14.jpg\"><img alt=\"1\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/14.jpg\" width=\"427\" height=\"332\" /></a><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-283286\" alt=\"2\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/24.jpg\" width=\"441\" height=\"298\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/24.jpg 441w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/24-300x202.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 441px) 100vw, 441px\" /> <a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/14.jpg\"><br />\n</a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>相关：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/bbc-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd%e5%bd%93%e5%b1%80%e6%9a%b4%e5%8a%9b%e5%a4%84%e7%90%86%e4%b8%8a%e6%b5%a6%e5%9c%9f%e5%9c%b0%e7%ba%a0%e7%ba%b7/\" target=\"_blank\">BBC | 中国当局“暴力处理”上浦土地纠纷</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/03/bbc-%e5%ae%98%e6%96%b9%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%9a%e8%b0%88%e4%b8%8a%e6%b5%a6%e6%9d%91%e8%bf%9b%e5%b1%95-%e7%bd%91%e6%b0%91%e8%a2%ab%e5%99%a4%e5%a3%b0/\" target=\"_blank\">BBC | 官方微博谈上浦村进展 网民被噤声</a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,21627,13770],"tags":[22505,22492,15021,13804]}